- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper compares different control mechanisms for resource management, which is related to systems and control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper mentions autonomic computing, which is related to AI. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper proposes an economic model for cloud resource management, which falls under the scope of this sub-category.
